Private investigator Paul O&#8217;Sullivan has been arrested. O&#8217;Sullivan s lawyer, Willie Spies confirmed the arrest but could not divulge the details of the charges. We have not been showed the charges yet. Arrest is unlawful and contravention of High court order. We will be in court tonight, said Spies.Spies said his client should have been given 48 hours before he was arrested.Inside the Pretoria High Court where Paul O&#8217;Sullivan&#8217;s legal team is about to launch an urgent court application. 